      Vector ParametrisedGeneType.createGeneVector(java.util.Random random)
      Returns an immutable Vector with metadata set to ParametrisedGeneType.getParamsGene() and with random values distributed uniformly between their minimum and maximum values (inclusive).

      Returns a mutable Vector with metadata set to ParametrisedGeneType.getParamsType() and with values initialised to zero.
